short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Brighten your day with an adorable Cute Kitten live wallpaper on every new Chrome tab.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Add a dose of cuteness to your browsing with the Cute Kitten live wallpaper Chrome extension. This extension fills your new tab with an irresistible kitten that’s perfect for anyone who loves charming, furry companions. With a chrome wallpaper that captures the kitten’s playful and sweet expressions, this is the ideal choice for chrome live wallpapers fans who want a cheerful touch every time they open a new tab.

This extension includes:

🐱 Live Wallpaper: Adorable kitten visuals in motion
🔎 Google Search Bar: Quickly search the web without leaving your new tab
🕒 Clock and Date Display: Track time with a stylish display
🔖 Adjustable Shortcuts: Easily add or remove your most-used sites

With a simple, cozy design, this chrome background extension makes every tab a moment of joy. Elevate your browsing experience with a touch of fluffiness and fun!
